Package ru.nsu.kiryushin

Class AdjListGraph<V>

java.lang.Object
ru.nsu.kiryushin.AdjListGraph<V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Graph<V>
public class AdjListGraph<V> extends Object implements Graph<V>
Graph implementation backed by adjacency lists. Vertices are stored in a set, each vertex keeps a list of outgoing neighbours. Supports directed/undirected graphs and multiedges via duplicated entries.
